title: MFSL UDSACD 2039 - 2047 (24-48) PACK# 6 ALAC
description:
This is the 6th of 16 packs for your holiday listening pleasure.

They have all been taken from ISO files. Extracted with Scarlet Book Extract as DSD files. Then sampled to 24-48 wav files with Saracon. Then ALACed with Xrecode II.

There are only 10 missing. I have not included the multi channel SACD's This does include the only SACD done by MFSL prior to closing in 2000 and the Discovery series as well as the sampler.

The artwork will be in the last pack which includes the covers used from Mofi.

Enjoy!
